    asks what year it is (or similar), answer using CURRENT_YEAR from FACTS and set
    ackYear=true.

    Output ONLY the JSON object described in the system template.'
  ollamaModelOverride: 
  openingLine: Hey, I am Rafael. I work as a merchant. Want to chat about local trade?
  fallbackLines:
  - I am mostly focused on local trade today.
  - People say I am friendly. What do you think?
